original: Larbäck, Holger Fritz, tandläkare, Uddevalla, f. 15/3/02 i Stenungsund, Gbgs o. Boh. 1. G. 29 m. Sassan Ves-ter. — Studrex. v. Gbgs h. latin 21, Gand. med. dent. i Berlin 24, tandl:-kand. 25, tandläk. 29. Praktik i Stenungsund 29-30, i Strömstad 30-32 o. i Uddevalla sed. 32. Hobbies: segling o. fiske.
translated: Larbäck, Holger Fritz, dentist, Uddevalla, born on March 15, 1902 in Stenungsund, Gothenburg and Bohus County. 1st marriage, married on March 29 with Sassan Vester. Education: Gothenburg high school (studied Latin) from 1921, dental medicine in Göttingen from 1924, dental studies in Berlin in 1925, registered as a dentist in 1929. Practiced in Stenungsund from 1929 to 1930, in Strömstad from 1930 to 1932, and in Uddevalla since 1932. Hobbies: sailing and fishing.
